<item>
            <title>[HIVE-1980] Merging using mapreduce rather than map-only job failed in case of dynamic partition inserts</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HIVE-1980</link>
                <project id="12310843" key="HIVE">Hive</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In dynamic partition insert and if merge is set to true and hive.mergejob.maponly=false, the merge MapReduce job will fail. &lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12498166">HIVE-1980</key>
            <summary>Merging using mapreduce rather than map-only job failed in case of dynamic partition inserts</summary>
